data.description: This is a nice, cozy starter home. The master bedroom has new carpet. Bathroom has been updated. Rooms have fresh coat of paint.  From the family room walk out to a covered private porch. The utility room doubles as a mudroom. Ample places to park, driveway and area near the street. Multiple entries with porches. The utility shed is 14x16. This home is USDA approved.
